The {{nihongo|'''Yangon Japanese School''' ('''YJS''')|ヤンゴン日本人学校|Yangon Nihonjin Gakkō}}, previously the {{nihongo|'''Rangoon Japanese School'''|ラングーン日本人学校|''Rangūn Nihonjin Gakkō}}, is a [[Nihonjin gakko|Japanese international school]] in [[Dagon Township]], [[Yangon]], [[Burma]].<ref>"[http://www.mext.go.jp/a_menu/shotou/clarinet/002/006/001/001/001.htm アジアの日本人学校一覧（平成25年4月15日現在）]." ([https://archive.is/3wyBZ Archive]) [[Ministry of Education, Culture, Sports, Science and Technology]]. Retrieved on 6 January 2014. "No.1, Thantaman Road, Dagon T/S, Yangon, MYANMAR"</ref>

